Community Tools Drush makefiles

Usage:

For 6.x development branch:

drush make https://github.com/kristjanjansen/cmtls_make/blob/6.x/cmtls.make sitename

For 6.x 0.5 release:

~~~
drush make https://github.com/kristjanjansen/cmtls_make/blob/6.x-0.5/cmtls.make sitename
~~~

For 7.x development branch:

drush make https://github.com/kristjanjansen/cmtls_make/blob/7.x/cmtls.make sitename

For 7.x experiments:

drush make https://github.com/kristjanjansen/cmtls_make/blob/7.x-experiments/cmtls.make sitename
